  "ai_usage": "Use for image galleries and pin boards where item heights vary and exact order doesn't matter. Set columns: column-width Npx (fluid) or N (fixed) on the container, column-gap for gutters, and break-inside: avoid + margin-bottom on each item. Caveat: items fill top-to-bottom per column, so it's not left-to-right reading order — use a JS lib or future native grid masonry if order matters.",
